-- India’s Sahara Group Buys Grosvenor House Hotel in London
-- B y   A b h a y   S i n g h
-- 2010-12-30T14:30:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-30/royal-bank-of-scotland-sells-london-hotel-to-sahara-group-for-725-million.html
India’s Sahara Group bought the
Grosvenor House hotel in London from the Royal Bank of Scotland
Group Plc for 470 million pounds, Sahara said in an e-mailed
statement today.  Sahara will add new restaurants, a night club, a business
center and a swimming pool to the property, the statement said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Abhay Singh at 
 abhaysingh@bloomberg.net  